				<input type="radio" name="zoom_and" value="0" checked="checked" />Cualquier palabra
				<input type="radio" name="zoom_and" value="1" />Todas las palabras - <a href="http://www.andinia.com/addurlsp.html">Agregar sitio</a>
			</form></p>
		</div>
        <div class="barra_azul fina">

